<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Harmonie Yacht — Infrastructure IA</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;600;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--bg:#050B18;--surface:#0A1628;--card:#0F1D35;--border:rgba(255,255,255,.06);--text:#E8E6E1;--muted:#8A8B8E;--gold:#D4A853;--gold-glow:rgba(212,168,83,.15);--green:#34D399;--blue:#60A5FA;--red:#F87171;--serif:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;--sans:'DM Sans',-apple-system,sans-serif}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body{font-family:var(--sans);background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);overflow-x:hidden;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}::selection{background:var(--gold);color:var(--bg)}
a{color:var(--gold);text-decoration:none}

/* Grain overlay */
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;background:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.03'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");pointer-events:none;z-index:9999}

/* Layout */
.container{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px}
section{padding:100px 0}

/* Reveal animation */
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:all .8s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1)}.reveal.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}

/* ===== HERO ===== */
.hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-200px;right:-200px;width:600px;height:600px;background:radial-gradient(circle,var(--gold-glow) 0%,transparent 70%);border-radius:50%}
.hero-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);border:1px solid rgba(212,168,83,.25);padding:8px 20px;border-radius:40px;margin-bottom:32px}
.hero h1{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(36px,6vw,72px);font-weight:500;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:24px;max-width:800px}
.hero h1 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--gold)}
.hero-sub{font-size:18px;color:var(--muted);max-width:560px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:48px}
.hero-metrics{display:flex;gap:48px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.metric{text-align:left}.metric .num{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:42px;font-weight:600;color:var(--gold)}.metric .label{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:4px}

/* ===== SECTION TITLES ===== */
.section-label{font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:12px}
.section-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,44px);font-weight:500;margin-bottom:20px;line-height:1.2}
.section-desc{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);max-width:600px;line-height:1.7}

/* ===== BEFORE/AFTER ===== */
.compare{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:32px;margin-top:48px}
.compare-card{padding:36px;border-radius:16px;border:1px solid var(--border)}
.compare-card.before{background:rgba(248,113,113,.04);border-color:rgba(248,113,113,.15)}
.compare-card.after{background:rgba(52,211,153,.04);border-color:rgba(52,211,153,.15)}
.compare-card h3{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:22px;margin-bottom:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.compare-card.before h3{color:var(--red)}.compare-card.after h3{color:var(--green)}
.compare-item{padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;line-height:1.5}
.compare-item:last-child{border:none}
.compare-item .icon{font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0}

/* ===== AGENTS ===== */
.agents-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px;margin-top:48px}
.agent-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:32px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:all .4s ease}
.agent-card:hover{border-color:rgba(212,168,83,.3);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.agent-card.full{grid-column:1/-1}
.agent-status{position:absolute;top:20px;right:20px;width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%}
.agent-status.active{background:var(--green);box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(52,211,153,.4)}
.agent-status.building{background:var(--gold);box-shadow:0 0 12px var(--gold-glow)}
.agent-status.planned{background:var(--muted)}
.agent-emoji{font-size:36px;margin-bottom:16px}
.agent-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:22px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:6px}
.agent-role{font-size:13px;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:16px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em}
.agent-desc{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px}
.agent-features{list-style:none;font-size:13px;color:var(--text)}
.agent-features li{padding:6px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.agent-features li::before{content:'→';color:var(--gold);font-weight:600}

/* ===== PIPELINE ===== */
.pipeline{margin-top:48px}
.pipe-step{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:24px;padding:24px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.pipe-step:last-child{border:none}
.pipe-num{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:36px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(212,168,83,.2);min-width:50px}
.pipe-content h4{font-size:16px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:6px}.pipe-content p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}
.pipe-tool{display:inline-block;font-size:11px;background:var(--gold-glow);color:var(--gold);padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;margin-top:8px}

/* ===== RESULTS ===== */
.results-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:20px;margin-top:48px}
.result-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:28px;text-align:center}
.result-card .num{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:40px;font-weight:600;color:var(--gold)}
.result-card .label{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:8px;line-height:1.4}

/* ===== STACK ===== */
.stack-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;margin-top:48px}
.stack-item{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px}
.stack-icon{font-size:28px;flex-shrink:0}
.stack-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:500}.stack-role{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}

/* ===== CTA ===== */
.cta{text-align:center;padding:120px 0;position:relative}
.cta::before{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:600px;height:400px;background:radial-gradient(circle,var(--gold-glow) 0%,transparent 70%)}
.cta-btn{display:inline-block;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:var(--bg);background:var(--gold);padding:16px 40px;border-radius:50px;text-decoration:none;transition:all .3s ease;position:relative}
.cta-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(212,168,83,.3)}

/* Footer */
footer{text-align:center;padding:40px 0;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);border-top:1px solid var(--border)}

/* Responsive */
@media(max-width:768px){
  section{padding:60px 0}
  .compare,.agents-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .agent-card.full{grid-column:auto}
  .results-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .stack-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .hero-metrics{gap:28px}
  .metric .num{font-size:30px}
  .pipe-step{flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-tag reveal">Infrastructure IA — Harmonie Yacht</div>
    <h1 class="reveal">Une <em>équipe d'agents IA</em> qui gère vos clients, vos finances et vos relances</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub reveal">Pendant que vous vivez, l'IA répond aux clients en moins de 5 secondes, classe vos dépenses par message vocal, et vous prévient quand il faut relancer un prospect.</p>
    <div class="hero-metrics reveal">
      <div class="metric"><div class="num">24/7</div><div class="label">Disponibilité commerciale</div></div>
      <div class="metric"><div class="num">&lt;5s</div><div class="label">Temps de réponse client</div></div>
      <div class="metric"><div class="num">4</div><div class="label">Agents IA actifs</div></div>
      <div class="metric"><div class="num">~50€</div><div class="label">Coût mensuel total</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- LE PROBLÈME -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
